column5: Floating point numbers should not be tested for equality
column6: Public methods should throw at most one checked exception
column10: Classes that override "clone" should be "Cloneable" and call "super.clone()"
column13: Loggers should be "private static final" and should share a naming convention
column23: Strings literals should be placed on the left side
column25: Control flow statements should not be nested too deeply
column35: Classes should not be compared by name
